ğŸš— Lane Detection System

A Python project that detects and highlights road lane markings in real time using OpenCV.
It captures video frames, processes them through edge detection and masking, and draws lane lines for better visual guidance.

ğŸš€ Features

âœ… Detects lane lines from video or webcam feed
âœ… Uses Canny edge detection and Hough Transform
âœ… Works on curved or straight roads
âœ… Visualizes detected lanes on each frame
âœ… Option to save sample input/output frames
âœ… Lightweight and easy to run on any system

